  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 5f7201a12d95ffc409449d95f23cf332, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: UnityEngine.UI::UnityEngine.UI.Text
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 0, g: 0, b: 0, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_FontData:
    m_Font: {fileID: 10102, guid: 0000000000000000e000000000000000, type: 0}
    m_FontSize: 45
    m_FontStyle: 0
    m_BestFit: 0
    m_MinSize: 10
    m_MaxSize: 45
    m_Alignment: 0
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'TERMS OF SUFFERING


    1. By accepting these terms, you agree to forfeit
    your sanity completely and absolutely.


    2. The developer reserves the right
    to mock you relentlessly in the event of any and all failures.


    3. You shall
    not complain about unfair mechanics on any social media platform.


    4. If
    you fail, it is a skill issue. Legally and morally.


    5. You must read this
    entire document, even though we both know you are just skimming.


    6. By
    continuing, you agree that Pineapple belongs on pizza. Non-negotiable.


    7.
    You hereby grant us permission to use your tears to salt our popcorn during movie
    nights.


    8. If you break your phone in rage, we are not liable. Your anger
    issues are your own personal demons to fight.


    9. Every time you die in
    this game, a kitten gets slightly annoyed somewhere in the world.


    10. You
    confirm you are not a robot, although your repetitive failures suggest otherwise.


    11.
    We reserve the right to change these terms whenever we feel like it, specifically
    to make you suffer more.


    12. In accordance with Subsection 4, Paragraph
    B: Any attempt to cheat, glitch, or bypass mechanics will result in immediate
    judgment by the code.


    13. We do not collect your personal data, because
    frankly, your gameplay data is embarrassing enough.


    14. Are you actually
    still reading this? This is why you don''t have a girlfriend.


    15. We are
    legally obligated to inform you of the following mechanical change: Upon returning
    from this agreement, the functionality of the Accept and Decline buttons will
    be entirely reversed.


    16. Any damage caused to your device by throwing
    it against a wall is strictly your responsibility and will not be reimbursed.


    17.
    Seriously, go outside. Touch some grass. Get some vitamin D.


    18. The left
    button was red, the right button was green. Did you memorize that? Good.


    19.
    By checking the box below, you swear under penalty of perjury that you read all
    of this. We both know you''re a liar.


    20. If you survived reading all this,
    you deserve a medal. But you won''t get one. Just pain.'
--- !u!222 &1385985227
